Package edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActorInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Actor, Allosaur, Brachiosaur, Dinosaur, Player, Pterodactyl, Stegosaur
public interface ActorInterface
This interface provides the ability to add methods to Actor, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    Corpse getCorpse()
    Creates and returns the corpse of the Actor.
    default java.lang.Integer getHitPoints()
    Returns the Actor's current hit points.
    default java.lang.Integer getMaxHitPoints()
    Returns the Actor's max hit points.
